    PROC & PEOPLE & TOOLS & GOV & CULTURE --> RADAR
    RADAR --> GAP
    GAP --> ROAD
    ROAD --> INV

    %% Cross-refs
    SETUP["PMO Setup"]:::dark
    ASSESS["PMO Assessment"]:::dark
    ROAD -.->|"informs"| SETUP
    ASSESS -.->|"strategic layer"| MAT
